rComments: I thought Dalton was a great teacher.  He was always prepared .  I think between enjoying the class and enjoying looking at him, I would do it again. He is very hot!!!  I think he is married, although I don't recall him wearing a ring.
Just go to discussion and participate. No suprises on exams. Everything discussed in class is on there. Very nice and easy going teacher... would take another class of his.

Very good teacher, gives clear interpretations of literature so you know how to answer essay questions but also listens to student interpretations.  Two five-page papers, a midterm, a final, and class participation make up the grade.  Go to his office hours and he will help you organize your essays.
